# Amara & Partners Website -- Cursor AI Rules

## Project Overview
- Professional legal consultancy website for Amara & Partners Legal Consultants
- Based in Abu Dhabi, UAE. Offices on Reem Island.
- Built with Next.js 15 (App Router), Tailwind CSS, and TypeScript
- Design tone: modern, approachable, premium, trustworthy
- Inspired visually by aoshearman.com -- adapted for boutique firm positioning

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js 15 with App Router
- Language: TypeScript -- always use proper types, never use `any`
- Styling: Tailwind CSS only -- never write plain CSS unless unavoidable
- Animations: GSAP + ScrollTrigger for scroll-driven effects, Framer Motion for UI transitions
- Deployment: Vercel (production), Dokploy (staging)
- CMS: To be decided later -- build frontend with static/placeholder data for now

