## Typography
- Headings: Cormorant Garamond (Google Fonts) -- weights 400, 500, 600
- Body: DM Sans (Google Fonts) -- weights 400, 500, 700
- Loaded via next/font (self-hosted, zero external requests)
- Type scale:
  - H1: 32px/36px, Bold, tracking-wide
  - H2: 24px/30px, Medium, tracking-normal
  - H3: 20px/26px, Regular
  - Body: 16px/24px Regular
  - Small: 14px/20px Regular

